metadata.name: BURWAI
metadata.description:
" I always chase the light "

This valley is located in the Naran Valley and near the famous Lake Saiful Muluk on the road which connects the KPK with Gilgit-Baltistan Babusar Pass. 

Body  : Nikon D850
Lens  : Nikon 70-200mm F4
Camera Settings : ISO- 100, 1200 Sec , F9
Dimension : 4482*2521
Location : Naran , Pakistan
